Class LinkConnectionStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.o3dr.services.android.lib.gcs.link.LinkConnectionStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public final class LinkConnectionStatus
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Conveys information about the link connection state.

    This value is returned in the Drone.notifyAttributeUpdated(java.lang.String, android.os.Bundle) as the extra value LinkEventExtra.EXTRA_CONNECTION_STATUS when the attribute event is LinkEvent.LINK_STATE_UPDATED
